 rtable walking and standing in line. You‚Äôre always welcome to leave at a
 ny time if you need to peel off early.\nThis is part food crawl\, part cit
 y walk\, part social adventure.\n\n\\*\\*\\*\n\nūüíį Important Notes\nMemb
 ers are responsible for purchasing their own cookies.\nMany cookies are la
 rge ‚ÄĒ sharing is encouraged! Split with a new friend. Build community th
 rough butter and sugar.\nBring cash\, as some spots may prefer it.\n\n\\*\
 \*\\*\n\nūüßĘ Meetup Details\nūüďć Meetup Location: Outside The Night Bake
 r\nūüęé I‚Äôll be wearing my Moose Hat\n‚Źį Meetup Time: 1:00 PM\n‚Ěó I wi
