 . Thank you for supporting community! ūüíĖ\n\n\\*\\*\\*\nūüĆą Who Is This 
 For?\nThis group is open to anyone who wants to be social and make friends
  ‚ÄĒ whether single or not.\nWe also host:\nūüé¨ Movies\nūüö∂ Walks & hike
 s\nūüé≠ Arts & culture outings\nūüćĹÔłŹ Restaurant socials\nBut today? Tod
 ay is about cookies.\n\n\\*\\*\\*\n\n‚ö†ÔłŹ A Gentle Reminder\nSometimes l
