 usic\, Movies\, Sports\, Fashion\, Hobbies\, Books\, Psychology\, Philosop
 hy\, the Future\, History\, Pop Culture\, Theatre\, etc.)\n\n**Arrival Tim
 e:**\n\\*Join us any time between 6:30 pm and 7:15 pm (if you can) for a f
